    • Method Detail

      • runRandomEffect

        public boolean runRandomEffect(boolean isRemote)
        Execute a random IDegradationEffect if the tick is at the correct value that as defined in getTickInterval(). Each time this method is called, the tick is increased.
        Parameters:
        isRemote - True for clients, false for servers.
        Returns:
        If a random effect was executed, can be false if the tick is too small or the randomly chosen effect can not be run.
